   <Parallels/>
   <Ritual>
   <Nerangs id="ritualNerangs">
      <ab>Y10.5 Var. a (mss. 5, 6, 40, 60, 88, 400, 2007, 2010, 2030, 2101, 4000, 4020, 4040, 5020):</ab>
      <ab class="ab_indent">
         az  <em>vīspə̄sca paiti varəšacīš vīspə̄sca paiti frasarəγə̄ vīspə̄sca paiti frauuāxšə̄</em>.  dō bār harw dō bār rāspīg-iz abāg zōt bē gōwišn bōy ō ī ātaxš dahišn </ab>
      <ab class="ab_indent">
         "From <em>vīspə̄sca paiti varəšacīš vīspə̄sca paiti frasarəγə̄ vīspə̄sca paiti frauuāxšə̄</em> they have to recite it twice. 
         The <em>rāspīg</em> has also to recite it together with the <em>zōt</em>. He has to give <em>bōy</em> to the fire."</ab>
      <ab>Y10.5 Var. b (mss. 2040, 4010, 4020, 4025, 4040, 4050, 4055, 4060, 4063, 4161, 4162, 4030a):</ab>
      <ab class="ab_indent">
         ... <em>frauuāxšə̄</em> harw dō bār bōy ōy ī ātaxš dahišn ud rāspīg-iz abāg zōt bē gōwišn </ab> 
      <ab class="ab_indent">
         "... <em>frauuāxšə̄</em> Each of the two times, he has to give <em>bōy</em> to the fire. The <em>rāspīg</em> has also to recite (the text) together with the <em>zōt</em>."</ab>
   </Nerangs>
